      "widgets_values": [
        "QUICK PARAMETERS PANEL\n\n**Noisy first frames:** With **no init image**, the sampler uses **full denoise on frame 0** (normal Deforum+Comfy path), then **scheduled strength** on later frames \u2014 so the start looks wild until the chain stabilizes. Mitigations here: **more steps early** (#14 `0:(10)` \u2192 `6:(8)` \u2192 `24:(6)`), **softer noise/contrast ramps** (#3), **gentler strength** on frames 1\u20132 (`0.30` after frame 0 in schedule), **`fixed` seed** (#2) for calmer first frame. For the **calmest** start, set **#8 use_init = Yes** and put a **neutral 960\u00d7540 PNG** at `input/continue_last.png` (or your `init_image` path).\n\n**SDXL Turbo:** euler + sgm_uniform, CFG 1.0, **#23** CLIP -2, **#22** sharpen. **LoRA:** #18 CLIP \u2192 #23 \u2192 #9 when using #17/#18.\n\n**Resolution / encode:** 960\u00d7540 (or 960\u00d7544); VHS yuv422p CRF 7. CONTINUE: #19 / #20 / #15 / #8."
      ],
